                    "body": "Tested with batch size = 2M and 4K. Latency changes as expected, and 4K significantly hurts throughput.\r\n Interestingly, 2M doesn't improve throughput, actually lower than 128K.\r\nPerf shows most CPU time spent in kernel mode copying data to/from user space. Too large batch size doesn't help.\r\n\r\n!flight-skylake-2M.png|width=890,height=336!\r\n\r\n!flight-skylake-4k.png|width=890,height=336!",
